<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Visualize the Universe - CS 594 Final Project</title>
    {{>head}}
    <script type="text/javascript">
      $(function(){
        $("#cmap").change(function(){
          $("#dark-matter-density-vid-src").attr("src", "/video/" + $(this).val() + ".mp4");
          $("#dark-matter-density-vid").load();
        });
      });
    </script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="page-container">
      {{> top_nav}}
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row row-offcanvas row-offcanvas-left">
          {{> sidebar}}
          <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-9" data-spy="scroll" data-target="#sidebar-nav">
            <h1>Results</h1>

            <div class="panel panel-default">
              <div class="panel-heading">Dark Matter Density over Time</div>
              <div class="panel-body">
                <p>This visualization uses the time sequenced data files found <a href="http://darksky.slac.stanford.edu/scivis2015/data/ds14_scivis_0128/">here</a>, creating an x-axis projection of the dark matter density for each file. The images are combined at a framerate of 10 FPS (frames per second) to create a video. Created using yt and varying color maps. You can change the color map in the dropdown below - I think green was my favorite, so that's the default.</p>
                <label for="cmap">Color Map</label>
                <select name="cmap" id="cmap">
                  <option value="withLegend">With Legend</option>
                  <option value="PRISM_r">Prism</option>
                  <option value="STD_GAMMA-II">Standard Gamma II</option>
                  <option value="afmhot">AFM Hot</option>
                  <option value="beach">Beach</option>
                  <option value="blue">Blue</option>
                  <option value="green" selected="selected">Green</option>
                </select>
                <br>
                <video id="dark-matter-density-vid" controls>
                    <source id="dark-matter-density-vid-src" src="/video/green.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                </video>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {{> footer}}
  </body>
</html>